{"id":280621,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-快讯：呼吁官员财产公示公民全国行/","date":"2013-02-24T07:45:51Z","modified":"2013-02-24T07:45:51Z","title":"维权网 | 快讯：“呼吁官员财产公示公民全国行”成员张昆在重庆遭扣押（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><span>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）本网早先曾予以报道的</span>呼吁官员财产公示公民全国行活动，</span><span>今日（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>星期日）在重庆遭警方阻拦，抢夺横幅、并扣押了公民行成员张昆（微博名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">@</span><span>多视角看世界）。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>奔走在全国各大城市，呼吁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">205</span><span>名中央委员公示财产的张昆和作家阮云华，今日上午在重庆解放碑新世纪广场打出宣传旗帜、横幅，征集公民签名。当张昆、阮云华在重庆街头呼吁官员财产公示征集签名时，突然被大批警力包围，抢走横幅和签名单，并发生扭打。张昆现在失去人身自由。他是被重庆市公安局渝中区分局交通巡逻警察一大队扣押的，警车已把他送到大阳沟派出所。同行的作家阮云华突破人群已经冲出。阮云华电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18671161336</span><span>、张昆电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18205002002</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网将会密切关注</span><span>“官员财产公示公民全国行”成员的随后情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZQ0fAG0Essg/USm3Ypu6HVI/AAAAAAAAdzY/svIZuoxG4QI/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130224144629.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"336\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZQ0fAG0Essg/USm3Ypu6HVI/AAAAAAAAdzY/svIZuoxG4QI/s400/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130224144629.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-I-EOGi3DynM/USm353upbWI/AAAAAAAAdzg/QIufvsaLnvk/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130224144853.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-I-EOGi3DynM/USm353upbWI/AAAAAAAAdzg/QIufvsaLnvk/s400/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130224144853.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}